  "ComponentName": "E55 'Spotlight' Illuminator",
  "LongDescription": "A radar transmitter that deploys a high-power cone in a direction for the purpose of guiding semi-active missiles.  A side-effect of this is the boosting of the target's radar signature, making the target easier to see.\n\nThe Spotlight deploys a long but narrow beam.",
